dct_title_s: Kyrgyzstan, travel map : an oasis on the Great Silk Road / [Raritet].
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, gradient tints, hachures, and spot heights. Panel title. Includes index to points of interest, index of administrative region names, time-zone directory, location map (inset), and color illustrations. Text, directories, statistical tables, and color illustrations on verso.
dct_publisher_sm: Bishkek : "Rarity" Firm LTD, [2001?] (Istanbul : Printed by "Mega Basim").
